    <span class="tt">randint(1..100)*10</span>\
 </li><li> 0 与 2 之间的十进小数:\
    <span class="tt">random(0..2)</span>\
 </li><li>表中的随机项:\
    <span class="tt">randitem(a,b,c,10,100,word,a phrase)</span>\
 </li></ul>

